import React from 'react'

import {
  Container,
  ImageContainer,
  FormContainer,
  Footer,
  Navbar,
  LogoContainer,
  Logo,
  Navigation,
  Select,
  HomeLink,
  SelectOption
} from './HomeStyles'

import LogoIcon from '../images/pubg.png'

export default function Home(props) {
  const handleClick = e => {
    let path = e.target.value
    props.history.push(`/leaderboards/${path}`)
  }

  return (
    <Container>
      <ImageContainer />
      <FormContainer />
      <Footer />
    </Container>
  )
}
